    section#features.features.bg-primary.text-center
      .container
        .row
          .col-lg-12.text-center
            .section-heading
              h2 Grow global &ndash; get locized
              p
                | Find out what locize can offer to make your localization experience a success story.
              p
                | You will ask yourself how could you live with sending around translation files in the past.
              hr
        .row
          .col-md-12
            .container-fluid
              .row
                .col-md-6
                  .feature-item
                    .device-container
                      .device-mockup.macbook_2015.silver
                        .device
                          .screen
                            img.img-responsive(src='img/screenshots/screen/integrate.png', alt='')
                          .button
                    h3 Time saving up to 90%
                    p
                      | Dropping one line of code on your website is all needed to get started. All your content gets extracted and send to your locize project ready to be translated.
                    p
                      | Every change on your websites content gets instantly reflected on your locize project and vice versa.
                .col-md-6
                  .feature-item
                    .device-container
                      .device-mockup.macbook_2015.silver
                        .device
                          .screen
                            img.img-responsive(src='img/screenshots/screen/editor.png', alt='')
                    h3 Continuous Localization Lifecycle
                    p
                      | locize enables you to separate your development and translation process. Keep translating while the development adds new features to your project.
                    p
                      | Easily keep track of newly added segments. Never lose the overview over your translation progress.
              .row
                .col-md-6
                  .feature-item
                    .device-container
                      .device-mockup.macbook_2015.silver
                        .device
                          .screen
                            img.img-responsive(src='img/screenshots/screen/incontext_editor.png', alt='')
                    h3 Context Matters &mdash; InContext Editing
                    p
                      | Doing correct translations needs more information by providing context informations. The best context is always the place where the content is used - your website!
                    p
                      | Our incontext editor enables you to directly change your translations from inside your website.
                .col-md-6
                  .feature-item
                    .device-container
                      .device-mockup.macbook_2015.silver
                        .device
                          .screen
                            img.img-responsive(src='img/screenshots/screen/ordering.png', alt='')
                    h3 Translation Management
                    p
                      | You can translate your content by using our powerful editor. Invite your inhouse translators giving them the rights for just the languages needed.
                    p
                      | Needing extra help or prefer to completely outsourcing the work? Choose one of our translation service partners.
