                      | From our one liner scripts enabling localization to non developers to instrumeting with i18next, formatjs, polyglot, ...
                .col-md-6
                  .feature-item
                    i.icon-target.text-primary
                    h3 Risk free
                    p.text-muted
                      | In contrast to other solutions out there we built on most popular open source frameworks.
                    p.text-muted
                      | So if you ever plan to stop using locize your translations could be used by i18next, formatjs or polyglot. Nothing is lost.
                    p.text-muted
